name: heart-shaped boob challenge
description:
Here is the Lora for heart-shaped boob challenge !

The trigger word is heart-shaped boob challenge, the suggested weight is 0.6 - 1

In this version, there is error of extra nipples, you may adjust the weight of the Lora to fine tune the result.

Hope you enjoy my work

You are welcome to browser my other works if you are interested!
